data.description: In WALKING distance to Indian Lake Beach, on a dead-end street, in the highly sought neighborhood, holds this BEAUTIFUL bungalow with lots of curb appeal! Updates galore, truly move-in ready, and can be fully furnished for the right price! Newer hot water heater. BEAUTIFUL deck and patio areas contained in the fully fenced-in yard. All rooms are spacious, updated kitchen island with seating for your eat-in kitchen which flows easily into the dining and living rooms areas for entertaining. A 3-season porch leads to the yard for a great space for reading with your morning coffee or as a TV/playroom. A small office in the front of the home is ideal for working from home. Upstairs the three bedrooms are sunny and have loads of closet space. The full bathroom on the second floor, half bath on the main level, and another full bathroom in the basement with the bonus room AND laundry!!  Great access to 290/190...THIS BEAUTY WILL NOT LAST LONG!!!
